    comment: CW carrier symbols transmitted before each data burst to let the radio
      stabilise. Value 4 maps to 0.0 Hz deviation (pure carrier). 5 symbols * (1/4800
      sym/s) = 1.04 ms. Carved out of the silence period so total frame length is
      unchanged.
    value: '2'
